[normal]partnership with Registered Social Landlords (RSLs) to develop a Housing Options 
[normal]              
[normal]shop which is scheduled to be op
[normal]erational during October 2013. The focus will be on 
[normal]              
[normal]supporting and facilitating exchanges where tenants have expressed and interest in 
