[normal]this.
[normal]2.7.
[normal] 
[normal]              
[normal]Invest in Renfrewshire is the Council’s flagship programme to tackle unemployment and 
[normal]              
[normal]improve employability wit
[normal]h in Renfrewshire. This programme
[normal]              
[normal] supported a Welfare 
[normal]              
[normal]Reform training programme within Housing Services for young people between the 
